		<title>11ISLAM IN NEWTON MEARNS</title>
		<content>    There is a population of about 3O  
 Mohammedan families in Newton Mearns  
                                       
      They have no place of worship in 
 the area. The nearest Mosque is one   
 newly opened in 1984 in the City of   
 Glasgow.                              
     Many of the children of these     
 families attend the local schools.    
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
